description: Southie for under a million! Just ten years young, this lovely two-bedroom, two-bathroom condo contains 1,126 sqft and is perfect for your everyday commuter or someone who likes to have it all close by! Some highlight features include an open floor plan, two capacious bedrooms, a designated outdoor deck, a secure intercom system w/video, and direct elevator entry. Additional storage can be stockpiled in the garage which contains one appointed parking spot. L Street is conveniently located off of E. Broadway Street which includes a variety of shops, cafes, restaurants, bars & more. If that isn't enough, the condo is positioned just minutes from the Seaport District, Boston's #1 attraction and neighborhood. Further amenities found close by are, L Street Beach, Castle Island, Medal of Honor Park, and South Station - just one stop to Downtown. 49 L is a perfect commute to almost anywhere with excellent admittance to I-93, I-90, & RT.1. or follow the Ted Williams Tunnel to Logan Airport.
